---
import Button from '../common/button.astro';
---

<section>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="content">
      <p class="tagline">Got Questions? We've Got Answers.</p>
      <h2 class="heading2">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="description">
        We know choosing the right partner for your web development needs is a big decision. Here are some common
        questions and answers to help you make the best choice.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li class="card white">
          <h3 class="heading3">How do you ensure my web app will be fast and scalable?</h3>
          <p class="body2">
            We use proven techniques and scalable design to make your app perform well in any conditions.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="card white">
          <h3 class="heading3">What if I only need help with part of my web app?</h3>
          <p class="body2">
            No problem! Our services are flexible and customizable, so we can work on just the areas where you need the
            most help.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="card white">
          <h3 class="heading3">Do you offer ongoing support?</h3>
          <p class="body2">Yes, we offer ongoing support and maintenance to keep your app updated and running well.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div>
        <Button href="/contact">Still Have Questions? Contact Us</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../../styles/abstracts' as *;

  section {
    background-color: $color-primary-light;
    padding-block: clamp(pxtorem(20), 4vw, pxtorem(70));
  }

  .content {
    display: grid;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding-inline: clamp(0%, 4vw, 25%);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-block-end: pxtorem(14);
  }

  .description {
    margin-block-end: clamp(pxtorem(20), 4vw, pxtorem(60));
  }

  ul {
    display: grid;
    gap: pxtorem(30);
    margin-inline: clamp(0rem, 4vw, pxtorem(200));
    margin-block-end: clamp(pxtorem(20), 4vw, pxtorem(50));
  }

  li {
    padding: pxtorem(40) pxtorem(88);

    h3 {
      margin-block-end: pxtorem(8);
    }
  }
</style>
